title: The Weather Girls Studio Album Discography
description:
The Weather Girls Studio Discography

This discography contains all of the studio albums produced by The Weather Girls, according to the Discogs and Wikipedia website listings. There are also four singles albums included, giving several versions of each song. The singles albums are mentioned below. All songs are in MP3 format and fully IDtagged for artist, album, and title. Songs for the following albums are included:

1980 The Weather Girls - Backatcha
1980 The Weather Girls - Two Tons o' Fun
1983 The Weather Girls - Success
1985 The Weather Girls - Big Girls Don't Cry
1988 The Weather Girls - Weather Girls
1993 The Weather Girls - Can U Feel It (Single)
1993 The Weather Girls - Double Tons of Fun
1993 The Weather Girls - We Shall All Be Free (Single)
1995 The Weather Girls - Oh What A Night (Single)
1998 The Weather Girls - Puttin' On The Hits
1999 The Weather Girls - Big Brown Girl (Single)
1995 The Weather Girls - Think Big
2007 The Weather Girls - Muscles, Men And More
2009 The Weather Girls - The Woman I Am
